def-en: In the context of the link prediction task, the task of predicting a subject to answer a link prediction query in the form $(?,p,o)$.
def-ga: I gcomhthéacs an taisc réamhinsinte nasc, an tasc a bhaineann le hainmní a réamhinsint chun ceist réamhinsinte nasc sa bhfoirm $(?,f,c)$ a fhreagairt.
notes: Féach chomh maith ar an téarma 'prediction / réamhinsint'.
